\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Core definition: Cybersecurity is the comprehensive practice of protecting computers, distributed networks, logical systems, and digital data sets from targets cyberattacks.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Primary Objective: The framework operates as a defensive perimeter to actively prevent unauthorized access from external hackers or distributed cybercriminals.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Methodology: Risk mitigation is achieved through a strategic combination of technology tools, administrative processes and ongoing security practices.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Business and Personal Value: Securing assets the continuity of operations and preserves individual privacy in an ecosystem where all entities are heavily reliant on data.
